data.description: Here is the home you have been looking for that can provide the staycation experience! This 3 bedroom, 3 1/2 bath can easily be a 4 bedroom/in-law arrangement utilizing the large room & full bath in the basement. Details abound including coffered ceilings, built-in furniture, detailed molding, spa-like master bathroom, with spacious walk-in closet. Plenty of space to gather inside and out. Deck replaced in 2022. The backyard is a retreat to itself with a deck, patio, gazebo & mature trees.
